                  <td width="333"><p class="style2">Health  and Human Services secretary Michael Leavitt, announcing the expedited  formation of a public/private organization to set ehealth record standards<a href="http://www.gcn.com/vol1_no1/daily-updates/36905-1.html">...Full Story</a></p></td>
